  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Pathology              : Provides a fundamental understanding of the diseases prevalent in North America, for upper level students in the biological sciences. Includes: general responses of cells and organ systems to injury; assessment of individual diseases by relating the causes, symptoms, diagnosis, treatment and prevention to the primary biological abnormalities in each disorder.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
