    <p>
      Microbiology and Immun (Sci)              : This course concentrates on the non-specific aspects of the immune response, an area which is not adequately covered by the other immunology courses presented at the university. Interactions between guest researchers (from McGill and other universities) and students will be furthered.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Winter 2015          </p>

